# Doki

Quantum computing simulation module, written in C.
Serves as the core of QSimov.
## Authors

* **Hernán Indíbil de la Cruz Calvo** - *Initial work* - [Mowstyl](https://github.com/Mowstyl)

See also the list of [contributors](https://github.com/Mowstyl/QDoki/contributors) who participated in this project.
